message: "If you use this lesson, please cite it as below."
title: "Agentic Research Workflows: AI Coding, Validation, and Research Responsibility"
abstract: "A Carpentries-style lesson on working with CLI-based AI coding agents in research without giving up the learning, validation, and judgment that make code trustworthy. Emphasizes a CLAUDE.md Living Spec, a four-layer validation stack, provenance, and responsible use."
